    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1884-09-03" rend="right">September 3 1884</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Mr Booth</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Thank you for sending me the volume <hi rend="italic">the Booths</hi>&#8212;It does
                not furnish me the picture I wanted&#8212;(I am very particular &#38; shall not be
                satisfied till I get one that fills the bill)&#8212;But the volume is more helpful
                to me (in touches, corrections, guidance &#38;c to my piece) than I can
                describe&#8212;&#38; the reading of all about your father, of absorbing
                interest&#8212;He was a beautiful character.<ptr target="loc.05827_n2"/></p>
            <closer><signed>Walt Whitman</signed></closer>

        </body>
